Package: funscoR
Type: Package
Title: Functional score calculation for phosphorylation sites 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: David Ochoa <ochoa@ebi.ac.uk>
Maintainer: David Ochoa <ochoa@ebi.ac.uk>
Description: Functional score calculation for phosphorylation sites.
    Given a list of phosphorylation sites, this package annotates them
    and provides a functional score based on a set of functional features.
License: LGPL
Encoding: UTF-8
